    "foot_0 At the end of the conversation, a binary outcome is observed.",
    "At turn i of a conversation consisting of messages c 1, m 1,.",
    ", c i, an AI agent assists the business by suggesting a message a i for the business to send to the customer (which the business representative may or may not adopt).",
    "We call this agent the SR agent foot_1.",
    "The SR agent may also abstain from making a suggestion (e.g., if it lacks sufficient knowledge to form a relevant suggestion), denoted as a i = ∅."
